overall word limit ~7000 words-8000 words

Introduction (~1700 words)

Think of 4 paragraphs for the intro, That's a rule of thumb.

Methods (~2200 words)

then methods and results (generally following one of my previous meta-analysis, e.g. the Gambusia one)

Results (~1700 words)

Discussion (~2000 words)

and then discussion 4-6 paragraph, with one being limitations.

